OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FThere will be varying, often
OL,6,Flarge amounts, of thin cloud but still
OL,7,Fwarm bright or sunny spells will
OL,8,Foccur. Slightly cooler along the coast
OL,9,Fwith onshore winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,12,Fand bright Saturday, warm or very
OL,13,Fwarm. Sunday sunny intervals and
OL,14,Fscattered showers, and feeling
OL,15,Fnoticeably cooler. Monday generally
OL,16,Fdry, with bright or sunny spells and
OL,17,Faverage temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
